
computers can also be called servers,pc, laptab,work station


Memory is measured in bytes

1 byte : 8 bits
1000 bytes : 1 kilo byte(kb) 10^3
1000kb : 1 megabyte(mb)10^6
1000Mb: 1 gigabyte(gb)10^9
===================================





editors:
notepad,sublime

Files:
content 
text
programming code
excutable code
special data(image,pdf,etc)

After file name we add extension so by looking at it we know what type of file it is
eg:
.txt
.pdf
.png
                                                     

